<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Lab – Amazon EC2</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0a0f1e;
      --surface: #101828;
      --border: #1e2d45;
      --accent: #f97316;
      --accent2: #38bdf8;
      --text: #e2e8f0;
      --muted: #64748b;
      --success: #22c55e;
      --mono: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      --sans: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--sans);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* Grid background */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(56,189,248,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(56,189,248,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 24px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
    }

    .badge {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .header-text {}

    .label {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: var(--accent2);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 46px);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    h1 span {
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .subtitle {
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
    }

    /* Status bar */
    .status-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: rgba(34,197,94,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.25);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 12px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--success);
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.8); }
    }

    .status-text { color: var(--success); }

    /* Section title */
    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent2);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .section-title::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }

    /* Intro block */
    .intro {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.15s ease both;
    }

    /* Steps */
    .steps {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .step {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 24px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease forwards;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .step:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent2);
      transform: translateX(4px);
    }

    .step:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .step:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
    .step:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .step:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .step:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }

    .step-num {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: rgba(249,115,22,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.3);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .step-content {}

    .step-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .step-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-family: var(--mono);
    }

    .step-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: rgba(56,189,248,0.1);
      color: var(--accent2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.2);
    }

    /* Skills grid */
    .skills-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.65s ease both;
    }

    .skill-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }

    .skill-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: rgba(249,115,22,0.05);
    }

    .skill-icon {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .skill-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.75s ease both;
    }

    .footer-left {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-badge {
      background: rgba(249,115,22,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.3);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* Code snippet in intro */
    code {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      background: rgba(56,189,248,0.1);
      color: var(--accent2);
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <span class="badge">AWS Lab</span>
      <div class="header-text">
        <div class="label">Cloud Computing // Amazon Web Services</div>
        <h1>Introduction to<br/><span>Amazon EC2</span></h1>
        <div class="subtitle">// Deploying & managing cloud virtual servers</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Status -->
    <div class="status-bar">
      <div class="dot"></div>
      <span class="status-text">EXERCISE SUCCESSFULLY COMPLETED AND VALIDATED</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <div class="section-title">Overview</div>
    <div class="intro">
      In this lab, I explored the fundamentals of <code>Amazon EC2</code> by deploying and managing a cloud-based virtual server.
      I launched an EC2 instance using <code>Amazon Linux 2023</code> and configured it as a simple web server using a User Data script
      that automatically installed and started the Apache web server. Once running, I monitored health and performance through
      the <code>EC2 dashboard</code> and <code>Amazon CloudWatch</code>.
    </div>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="section-title">Lab Steps</div>
    <div class="steps">

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">Launch & Configure EC2 Instance</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Launched an EC2 instance using Amazon Linux 2023. Configured it as a web server via a User Data script that automatically installed and started Apache.</div>
          <span class="step-tag">EC2 · Apache · User Data</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">Monitor Health & Performance</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Used the EC2 dashboard and Amazon CloudWatch to observe instance metrics and ensure the server was running correctly.</div>
          <span class="step-tag">CloudWatch · Monitoring</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">Configure Security Group & HTTP Access</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Updated inbound security group rules to allow HTTP traffic on port 80. Successfully accessed the hosted web page using the instance's public IPv4 address.</div>
          <span class="step-tag">Security Groups · Port 80 · IPv4</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">Resize Compute & Storage</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Resized the instance from <code>t3.micro</code> to <code>t3.small</code> and expanded the Amazon EBS storage volume from <code>8 GiB</code> to <code>10 GiB</code> to practice cloud scalability.</div>
          <span class="step-tag">Scaling · EBS · t3.small</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">05</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">Termination Protection & Lifecycle</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Tested termination protection to confirm it prevented accidental deletion. Then disabled the protection and terminated the instance to manage the full lifecycle.</div>
          <span class="step-tag">Termination Protection · Lifecycle</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Skills -->
    <div class="section-title">Key Skills Practiced</div>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-icon">🚀</div><div class="skill-label">Launching and configuring an EC2 instance</div></div>
      <div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-icon">🌐</div><div class="skill-label">Deploying a web server via User Data script</div></div>
      <div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-icon">🔒</div><div class="skill-label">Managing security groups and network access</div></div>
      <div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-icon">📊</div><div class="skill-label">Monitoring instance health and metrics</div></div>
      <div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-icon">⚖️</div><div class="skill-label">Resizing compute and storage resources</div></div>
      <div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-icon">🛡️</div><div class="skill-label">Testing termination protection & lifecycle</div></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-left">Amazon Web Services · EC2 Fundamentals Lab</div>
      <div class="footer-badge">✓ Validated</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
